earity, is likely\nlinked to variations of the emissivity of the spine.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Apr 2014 08:24:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Jun 2014 09:55:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
